## Base .gitignore pour .NET / ASP.NET Core

# Build et bin/obj
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/

# Build results
[Dd]ebug/
[Rr]elease/
x64/
x86/
artifacts/

# Logs
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/
*.log

# Packages NuGet
*.nupkg
*.snupkg
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# Rider / JetBrains
.idea/

# Coverage & Test
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
nunit-*.xml
*.VisualState.xml
Coverage/

# ASP.NET Core / EF
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt
appsettings*.json

# Temporary files
~$*
*~

# Node / npm (si tu as un frontend Angular dans le repo)
node_modules/
dist/
.tmp/
